     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts mappingAuteurCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"mappingAuteurCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcmappingAuteurCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-auteur</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-author</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td><td><b>Commentaire</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMAuteur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>author</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMAuteur.roleFonctionnel</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>author.functionCode</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMAuteur.horodatageParticipation</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>author.time</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMAuteur.FRLMPersonneStructure</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>author.assignedAuthor</td><td>L'élément PersonneStructure est de type PersonneStructure.</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMAuteur.FRLMSystemeStructureAuteur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>author.assignedAuthor</td><td>L'élément SystemeStructureAuteur est de type Systeme</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 2 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-author</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-composition-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td><td><b>Commentaire</b></td></tr><tr><td>author</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.author</td><td/></tr><tr><td>author.time</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.author.extension:time</td><td/></tr><tr><td>author.functionCode</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.author.PractitionerRole.code</td><td>Auteur du document est un professionnel et author.ofType(PractitionerRole)</td></tr><tr><td>author.assignedAuthor</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.author.Practitioner</td><td>Composition.author.resolve().ofType(Practitioner)</td></tr><tr><td>author.assignedAuthor</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.author.Patient</td><td>Composition.author.resolve().ofType(Patient)</td></tr><tr><td>author.assignedAuthor</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.author.Device</td><td>Composition.author.resolve().ofType(Device)</td></tr></table></div>"
